main event: Four orange objects and one white object appeared similar to an explosion and back together again. The objects appeared as flashing lights, moving like a yo-yo and fading as they went through a cloud.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for five to six minutes., The objects appeared east of the station., Observations were made visually from the ground., The nature of the sighting was considered semi-fantastic., The sighting was resolved as UNKNOWN and forwarded to ATIC for further assessment.
sighted object: four orange objects and one white object
